28#ifndef _SYS_VDEV_DISK_H
29#define _SYS_VDEV_DISK_H
30
31#include <sys/vdev.h>
32#ifdef _KERNEL
33#include <sys/buf.h>
34#include <sys/sunldi.h>
35#include <sys/sunddi.h>
36#endif
37
38#ifdef __cplusplus
39extern "C" {
40#endif
41
42#ifdef _KERNEL
43typedef struct vdev_disk {
44#ifdef illumos
45 ddi_devid_t vd_devid;
46 char *vd_minor;
47 ldi_handle_t vd_lh;
48 list_t vd_ldi_cbs;
49 boolean_t vd_ldi_offline;
50#endif
51#ifdef __NetBSD__
52 char *vd_minor;
53 vnode_t *vd_vp;
54 struct workqueue *vd_wq;
55 int vd_maxphys;
56#endif
57} vdev_disk_t;
58#endif
59
60extern int vdev_disk_physio(vdev_t *,
61 caddr_t, size_t, uint64_t, int, boolean_t);
62
63/*
64 * Since vdev_disk.c is not compiled into libzpool, this function should only be
65 * defined in the zfs kernel module.
66 */
67#ifdef _KERNEL
68extern int vdev_disk_ldi_physio(ldi_handle_t, caddr_t, size_t, uint64_t, int);
69#endif
70#ifdef __cplusplus
71}
72#endif
73
74#endif /* _SYS_VDEV_DISK_H */
